    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a pretty strong stance on what the \"consensus\" is. What about the economic side? Some people argue it's essentially just a regressive tax that hits people who live in outer boroughs or areas without good subway access the hardest. Can you explain why they feel that way?",
